text:
TAT presents awards to winners of One and Only Online Clip Competition
Mr. Yuthasak Supasorn, Governor, Tourism Authority of Thailand, presided over the award presentation ceremony of the ‘One and Only Online Clip Competition’ to present awards to winners in the student category and the public category.
The One and Only Online Clip Competition is under the Discover Thainess project, which promoting tourism matching the Thai ways of life.
The competition provides opportunities for students and publics to help promote Thailand’s attractions with new angles and urge continuous tourism in different regions of Thailand.
